### Skills.sh 爬虫 API 示例
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 或其他HTTP客户端测试

### 1. 获取技能爬虫使用说明
GET http://localhost:3002/skills
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 爬取 Skills.sh 前10个技能 (默认)
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 爬取 Skills.sh 前5个技能
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape?limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. 爬取指定的GitHub仓库技能信息
POST http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape-repos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositories": [
    "microsoft/github-copilot-for-azure",
    "inferen-sh/skills",
    "microsoft/azure-skills",
    "pbakaus/impeccable",
    "supercent-io/skills-template"
  ]
}

###

### 5. 爬取更多知名技能仓库
POST http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape-repos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositories": [
    "langchain-ai/langchain",
    "microsoft/autogen",
    "openai/openai-python",
    "anthropics/anthropic-sdk-python",
    "huggingface/transformers",
    "microsoft/semantic-kernel",
    "run-llama/llama_index",
    "microsoft/PromptCraft-Robotics"
  ]
}

###

### 6. 测试错误处理 - 超出限制
GET http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape?limit=100
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. 测试错误处理 - 无效仓库格式
POST http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape-repos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositories": []
}

###

### 8. 爬取特定AI技能相关仓库
POST http://localhost:3002/skills/scrape-repos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositories": [
    "guidance-ai/guidance",
    "microsoft/TaskWeaver",
    "microsoft/JARVIS",
    "yoheinakajima/babyagi",
    "Significant-Gravitas/Auto-GPT"
  ]
}

###